summary: Last summer my girlfriend and I have managed a small Glamping in Croatia. During this experience it has (again) been confirmed that I am made for the hospitality and leisure industry. So, I've found a new adventure as General Manager of Roompot Wijk aan Zee. Where I'll be responsible of managing a relatively big beach club and 50 accomodations on the beach.
